286
00:21:38.588 --> 00:21:41.842
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me.

287
00:21:41.925 --> 00:21:45.137
Please make Gi-tae fall in love with me!

288
00:21:46.722 --> 00:21:48.974
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me.

289
